Definition: characterized by intense emotion
Example: ardent love; an ardent lover; a fervent desire to change society; a fervent admirer; fiery oratory; an impassioned appeal; a torrid love affair
Synonyms: fervent, noun, feeling, fervency, fervid, fervidness, fiery, fire, attribute, fieriness, impassioned, perfervid, torrid, characterized, by, intense, emotion, love, an, lover, a, desire, to, change, society, admirer, oratory, appeal, affair
Category: adj.all
